msgid "# Werewolf _Medium humanoid (human, shapechanger), chaotic evil_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werewolf.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 11 in humanoid form, 12 (natural armor) in wolf or hybrid "
"form    \n"
"**Hit Points** 58 (9d8 + 18)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. (40 ft. in wolf form) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werewolf.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 15 (+2) | 13 (+1) | 14 (+2) | 10 (+0) | 11 (+0) | 10 (+0) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werewolf.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Perception +4, Stealth +3    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical "
"attacks not made with silvered weapons    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 14    \n"
"**Languages** Common (can't speak in wolf form)    \n"
"**Challenge** 3 (700 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werewolf.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Shapechanger.** The werewolf can use its action to polymorph into a "
"wolf-humanoid hybrid or into a wolf, or back into its true form, which is "
"humanoid. Its statistics, other than its AC, are the same in each form. Any "
"equipment it is wearing or carrying isn't transformed. It reverts to its "
"true form if it dies.    \n"
"**Keen Hearing and Smell.** The werewolf has advantage on Wisdom "
"(Perception) checks that rely on hearing or smell. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werewolf.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack. (Humanoid or Hybrid Form Only).** The werewolf makes two "
"attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws or spear.    \n"
"**Bite (Wolf or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach "
"5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage. If the target is a "
"humanoid, it must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or be cursed "
"with werewolf lycanthropy.    \n"
"**Claws. (Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 "
"ft., one creature. _Hit:_ 7 (2d4 + 2) slashing damage.    \n"
"**Spear (Humanoid Form Only).** _Melee or _Ranged Weapon Attack:__ +4 to "
"hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one creature. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) "
"piercing damage, or 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage if used with two hands to "
"make a melee attack.\n"
msgstr ""
